==Transport== [[National Highway 110 (India)|NH 110]] links Arwal to [[Bihar Sharif]] on [[National Highway 31 (India)|NH 31]]. National Highway 139 (old- NH 98) passes through Arwal connecting [[Aurangabad Bihar|Aurangabad]] to [[Patna]]. The nearest railway station is Jehanabad [[(JHD)]] at 35&nbsp;km and [[Anugraha Narayan Road railway station]] (AUBR)at 60&nbsp;km.
